  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is buffet-style with an excellent selection of hot and cold dishes. There will be fresh fruit in your room on arrival, and you'll receive a welcome drink too.</p>
<p>Packed lunches are available locally for a cost of around €7.50 per person per day.</p>
<p>In the evening, tuck into a five-course dinner with choices of main dish, a salad buffet and cheese.</p>
<p>On the 13th August, it's the annual Summer Festival in Lech and the Hotel Berghof will have many all-you-can-eat food stands and a DJ in the garden for a Garden Party. There is a surcharge of €20 per person (payable locally) which includes two drinks tokens. On this evening there is no half board meal.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
