  <description><![CDATA[<p>Just above the village centre and overlooking <a data-udi="umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0}" title="Lech">Lech</a> is the excellent Hotel Berghof. If you're looking for that perfect blend of trendiness and laid-back Austrian charm, your search ends here.</p>
<h2>Prime location</h2>
<p>If adventure's your thing you're in for a treat. The hotel has a privileged location, just a stone's throw from the Rüfikopf cable car. Step onto the cable car and up you go - a world of wonder awaits. The mountain offers an array of walking trails, including the legendary White Ring trail.</p>
<h2>Relax in the luxurious spa</h2>
<p>After a day of exploration, the hotel's spa invites you in for a little R&amp;R. Banish aching muscles with soothing saunas, a steam room, and an infrared cabin.</p>
<p>The Hotel Berghof is a testament to the art of hospitality, curated meticulously by its owners, Isabelle and Stefan Burger, and their dedicated team. The rooms are beautiful and thoughtfully designed, and the meals are excellent too.</p>]]></description>
